Raja Indradev Chauhan, Raaj krte the Dholakpur par. Waha rehti thi ek tawaif, naam tha uska Tun Tun, har admi jiski jeb mai paisa and patlung mein Khamba Tun Tun ka Tuntuna baja sakta tha. Raja Indradev un dino Rajkumar Hua krte the. Unki jeb mein bohot saara Dhan aur Patlung mein bahut bada Khamba tha. Unhe Tun Tun ke baare mein pta chala, toh woh waha bina kisi ko btaye waha padhaare. Tun Tun apne Golu Molu Dho rhi thi are Golu Molu par Indradev ki Nazar Padi. Ussi samay indradev ne apni Jeb se Paisa and apni Patlungse apna land nikala aur Tun Tun ka tuntuna bajane lga, uss raat Indradev ne apni puri tanki khali kar di. 9 mahine baad Tun Tun ke tuntune se Chutki Prakat hui. Raja Indradev Apna saara bal Chutki par lga chuke the, to sirf Indumati ko hi jan paye, aur iss tarah shuru hui Bheem aur chutki ki Love story
